WEBVTT

1
00:32:22.770 --> 00:32:24.020 
贝茨
Bates.

2
00:32:25.190 --> 00:32:29.110 
这位先生是卡森先生的熟人  小姐
This gentleman is an acquaintance of Mr Carson, my lady.

3
00:32:29.190 --> 00:32:30.940 
那他在这里做什么
What is he doing in here?

4
00:32:31.030 --> 00:32:33.450 
他说他找老爷有急事
He says he has urgent business with his lordship.

5
00:32:33.530 --> 00:32:34.780 
十万火急
Urgent.

6
00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:39.040 
我已经立马派人去叫卡森先生了
I've sent for Mr Carson to come at once.

7
00:32:39.370 --> 00:32:41.120 
那我和你一道留下
Then I'll stay with you

8
00:32:41.120 --> 00:32:43.340 
以防事后说不清楚
in case explanations are needed.

9
00:32:47.040 --> 00:32:48.920 
卡森先生
Mr Carson!

